snippet.title: 3DS Mod: Supernova Sun & Penumbra Moon!
snippet.description:
More Information + Links: http://diovento.wordpress.com/snspum

These mods are for Pokémon Ultra Sun and Pokémon Ultra Moon. They will not work with Sun and Moon. For my Sun and Moon hacks, check out Nova Sun and Umbra Moon here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f6vpz8i7nAY
